==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Smelling salts
<hw>Smell"ing salts</hw>. <def>An aromatic preparation of carbonate of
ammonia and, often, some scent, to avoid or relieve faintness, headache,
or the like.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Smell-less</ent>⟦br⟧
